# TASK: Adaptasi Source OpenClaw ke AgentAI01

## Konteks Project

**Project:** AgentAI01 — AI Company Runtime (multi-agent system)
**Stack:** Bun 1.3.x + TypeScript 5.8.x + Node 20+
**Module system:** ESM (`"type": "module"`)
**Referensi:** `referensi/openclaw/src/` (jangan diedit, hanya dibaca)

### Struktur Target AgentAI01

```
src/
├── domain/              # types + kontrak utama
├── agents/              # ceo, engineering, marketing, product, dll
├── runtime/             # runtime/orchestrator
├── runtime-app/
│   ├── speech/          # TTS / STT
│   ├── generation/      # image/file generation
│   ├── integration/     # koneksi sistem eksternal
│   ├── diagnostics/     # monitoring & logging
│   ├── orchestration/   # koordinasi antar agent
│   ├── providers/       # AI provider adapter
│   ├── queue/           # job queue
│   ├── skills/          # skill runner
│   ├── tools/           # tool definitions per agent
│   ├── workers/         # background workers
│   └── memory/          # memory layer
├── plugin-sdk/          # plugin system
├── provider-runtime/    # provider abstraction
├── memory/              # memory + storage
├── web-search/          # web search
└── web-fetch/           # web fetch + content extraction
```

